<h2>Diet & Patient Mess</h2>
<hr />
<span class="title">Module Overview </span><br />
<div class="clear"></div>
This module deals with the full-fledged Diet & Patient Mess management system.  The scope of the module covers Patient diet entry, Daily diet & extra requisition preparation, Diet Sheet Summary preparation based on all ward input, Breakfast distribution for walking & bed patient, Breakfast summary, Lunch/dinner distribution of Main cook house & Therapeutic cook house, Dry ration and fresh ration internal demand   etc.
The module maintains the Daily diet for ward, Daily summary for extras ward wise, Monthly summary for all wards, DRSS(Daily ration strength statement) report etc.

<br /><br />

<span class="title">In this Module has following Sub Modules </span>
<ol>
<li>Patient Diet Change</li>
<li>Daily Diet & Extra Requisition</li>
<li>Extra Items Formula</li>
<li>Menu Item Formula</li>
<li>Indent Item Formula</li>
<li>Internal Demand & Issue Voucher</li>
<li>Breakfast Distribution</li>
</ol>
